text: A majority of people want a new Covid-19 lockdown.
WHO issued proposal for extending lockdowns to control COVID-19
World Health Organization issues guidelines on COVID-19 lockdown
The government has issued guidelines to ease COVID-19 lockdown in India
Lockdown and the tier systems are deadlier than Covid-19.

The result of lockdowns has been the destruction of millions of lives across America as well as increased deaths from suicide, substance abuse and despair without any corresponding benefit in Covid mortality.
Says that shutdowns are ineffective and that we now know that COVID-19 is not commonly spread by someone going to work.
